    <h2>{`The Voting Contract`}</h2>
    <p>{`To vote, MKR owners must "lock-up" tokens by transferring them into the Voting Contract. Votes are weighted based on the quantity of MKR locked in the contract. "Locked" MKR can be withdrawn at any time.`}</p>
